<l n="d"><milestone unit="column" n="b"/>takkaṁ kr̥ṣṇā ca tāvatī</l>
</lg>
                   <lg n="30" met="anuṣṭubh">
<l n="a" enjamb="yes"><lb n="C11"/><milestone unit="column" n="a"/><g type="circleTarget">.</g> Ekaḥ pañca-palas siktha</l>
